There are no customers to have reported Food poisoning
 
in our restaurant till date. We have served nearly 1000's of customers
this  
year and not even 1 of them reported this issue. We are a restaurant with 

very high standards You can check our restaurant reviews on Toptable and  

Tripadvisor as well. The review posted seems like a message of hatred  
against the organisation. It can be from one of the competitors or any
sort  
of person who doesn't want to see the growth of business. Kindly look into
 
the matter and remove this on an urgent basis as it effects the working
and  
image of the organisation.
